"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1929587-bbc-olympics-eurosport-discovery-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  There is a very good reason why theBBCare unable to broadcast every single event from theParis Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Beeb's\\u00a0coverage has been significantly reduced from previous levels, both on television and online.\", \"from\": 112, \"to\": 215, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Social media users expressed their annoyance that the semi-finals of the men's 100m breaststroke, featuring champion Adam Peaty from 2016 and 2020, was not broadcast live.\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 344, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Peaty\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_Peaty\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While the corporation also faced a difficult decision on Sunday as Dan Evans and Andy Murray triumphed at Roland-Garros.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"score\": 0.9992127168936146, \"rank\": 0.0007879034091669758, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daniel_J._Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.55156333208273e-31, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC's Olympic content has been restricted in recent years due to a TV deal struck by Warner Brothers Discovery (WBD) in 2015.\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 515, \"end\": 518, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9527215691727868, \"rank\": 0.049546316855223836, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 606, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"score\": 0.999950620072974, \"rank\": 4.932322479350955e-05, \"text\": \"Warner\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WarnerMedia\"}, {\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.7975826738852786e-12, \"text\": \"Brothers\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brother\"}, {\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5635136719313796e-13, \"text\": \"Discovery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Discovery_Channel\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The American company purchased the European TV rights for the Games for \\u20ac1.3billion (\\u00a31.09bn), granting it comprehensive pick-and-choose live coverage of every sport across its channels, including TNT Sports, Eurosport and the Discovery+ app.\", \"from\": 641, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 641, \"end\": 661, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_American_Company\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The American company\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_American_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_American_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 838, \"end\": 848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.613773992718021e-40, \"text\": \"TNT Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Turner_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The fact that the BBC retains any rights at all is due to UK law, reportsthe Mirror.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 903, \"end\": 906, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9527215691727868, \"rank\": 0.049546316855223836, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9859563935822915, \"rank\": 0.013534874586213453, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the Olympics is considered a protected event, a national broadcaster is permitted to broadcast the Games on one linear channel, such as BBC One, and one digital channel, like iPlayer.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8509470990774376e-24, \"text\": \"BBC One\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_One\"}, {\"begin\": 1148, \"end\": 1155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their ability to broadcast the Olympics has taken a hit due to rights restrictions, with significant moments possibly being missed.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They explained their position on not securing complete rights for the Games on their website.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a statement uploaded online, they said: \\\"Quite simply because we take decisions over our spending very seriously as it is licence fee payers' money that we are using.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As much as we'd like to, we can not buy everything we want.\\\"\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1615, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For comprehensive coverage of the action, all 4,000 hours of it, enthusiasts must turn to the Discovery+ app.\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1726, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For those yet to join, Discovery+ is enticing Olympic fans with a deal until August 11, offering sign-ups at only \\u00a33.99 a month.\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1899, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1964, \"end\": 1969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2110558610316194e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 2075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2045, \"end\": 2057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9989129805660819, \"rank\": 0.0010882023309478131, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 2076, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Sky TV subscribers already enjoying Eurosport 1 and 2 can get a Discovery+ Standard Plan at no additional charge.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2145, \"end\": 2151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.996108240050053, \"rank\": 0.003906964894465838, \"text\": \"Sky TV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In more positive news for the BBC, there was a huge boost in viewership for the opening ceremony in comparison with the last two competitions.\", \"from\": 2259, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2289, \"end\": 2292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9527215691727868, \"rank\": 0.049546316855223836, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the poor weather, the ceremony in Paris boasted more BBC viewers than the past two Olympics combined.\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2445, \"end\": 2450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2110558610316194e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2464, \"end\": 2467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"score\": 0.9527215691727868, \"rank\": 0.049546316855223836, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Sport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A whopping 6.8m tuned in to watch Canadian icon Celine Dion serenade the audience with Edith Piaf's classic 'L'Hymne A L'Amour' from the Eiffel Tower, captivating audiences from 5.45pm to 10.40pm on BBC One.\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2547, \"end\": 2560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_symbols_of_Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian icon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_symbols_of_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_symbols_of_Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 2561, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0981087612324664e-39, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}, {\"begin\": 2600, \"end\": 2610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"score\": 0.9999999912251951, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Edith Piaf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2831, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  The peak viewing figure hit an impressive 7.9m, marking a high point in engagement since London 2012's grand opening, which attracted a staggering 22.4 million viewers.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3055, \"end\": 3066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999997963236845, \"rank\": 2.036762525166145e-07, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They were also aided by the minimal time difference as France stands just one hour ahead of the UK, compared to Brazil and Japan.\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3264, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3190, \"end\": 3196, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999982877976542, \"rank\": 1.4314086241767859e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3231, \"end\": 3233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9859563935822915, \"rank\": 0.013534874586213453, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3247, \"end\": 3253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"score\": 0.9999911440823926, \"rank\": 8.838821956523275e-06, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil\"}, {\"begin\": 3258, \"end\": 3263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9991888074849942, \"rank\": 0.0007504621771683633, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Rio de Janeiro, the ceremony started at midnight in the UK and attracted an average of 3.8 million viewers.\", \"from\"